HEADWORD: Excipient
<hw>Ex*cip"i*ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>excipients</ets>, <ets>-entis</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>exipere</ets>.
