==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Excipient
<hw>Ex*cip"i*ent</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An exceptor.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med., Pharmacy)</fld> <def>An inert or slightly
active substance used in preparing remedies as a vehicle or medium of
administration for the medicinal agents.</def>
<rj><au>Chambers.</au></rj></p>

<p><ent>Excipulum</ent>⟦br⟧
